wezterm.on("switch-font", function(window, pane)
	local current_font_index = current_font_index % #fonts + 1
	window:set_config_overrides({
		font = fonts[current_font_index],
	})
	window:toast_notification("Font Switched", "Now using font index " .. current_font_index, nil, 4000)

#!/usr/bin/env bash

WALLPAPER_DIR="$HOME/wallpapers/"
CURRENT_WALL=$(hyprctl hyprpaper listloaded)

# Get a random wallpaper that is not the current one
WALLPAPER=$(find "$WALLPAPER_DIR" -type f ! -name "$(basename "$CURRENT_WALL")" | shuf -n 1)

# Apply the selected wallpaper
hyprctl hyprpaper reload ,"$WALLPAPER"
